headline: Paycom Secures Payment Institution License from Central Bank of Ireland, Expanding European Payroll Capabilities
summary: OKLAHOMA CITY, May 01, 2025--Paycom Europe Limited, a subsidiary of Paycom Software, Inc. (NYSE: PAYC) ("Paycom"), a leading provider of comprehensive, cloud-based human capital management software, received authorization as a Payment Institution (PI) by the Central Bank of Ireland (CBI). This license presents future growth opportunities for Paycom across Europe.

headline: 2 S&P 500 Stocks for Long-Term Investors and 1 to Brush Off
summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is often seen as a benchmark for strong businesses, but that doesn’t mean every stock is worth owning. Some companies face significant challenges, whether it’s stagnating growth, heavy debt, or disruptive new competitors.
